text: The 2002 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 2002 NCAA Division I-A football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by first-year head coach Paul Johnson. ==Schedule== ==Roster== ==References== Navy Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen football
